Unit 2, Bexar County, Texas
Notice is hereby given that the above-described Property is encumbered and subject to
indebtedness owed to the lien holder by the Owner in the amount set forth above for due but unpaid
assessments, late fees, legal expenses, and filing fees, and that pursuant to the Declaration of Protective
Covenants for Sunset Subdivision, Unit 1, executed on October 14, 1999, recorded in Volume 8171, Page
1607, Official Public Records of Real Property of Bexar County, Texas, as amended by the First
Supplement to Declaration of Protective Covenants for Sunset Subdivision, Declaration of Annexation of
Sunset Subdivision, Unit 2, executed on May 31, 2000, recorded in Volume 8447, Page 1592, Official
Public Records of Real Property of Bexar County, Texas as amended, the lien holder has a Lien on the
Property described above for said sums.

Notice is further given that the amount of the Lien continues to increase pursuant to the terms of
the referenced Declaration.
